WEBVTT

00:07:57.374 --> 00:08:01.284
that too many of the machines
became concentrated

00:08:01.308 --> 00:08:04.588
in the hands of the government
or of a small elite.

00:08:05.109 --> 00:08:09.815
Now data is replacing
both land and machines

00:08:09.839 --> 00:08:11.950
as the most important asset.

00:08:12.600 --> 00:08:17.940
Politics becomes the struggle
to control the flows of data.

00:08:17.964 --> 00:08:20.672
And dictatorship now means

00:08:20.696 --> 00:08:26.476
that too much data is being concentrated
in the hands of the government

00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:28.420
or of a small elite.

00:08:28.871 --> 00:08:33.783
The greatest danger
that now faces liberal democracy